peid_packer;The executable uses a known packer;1;
pe_unknown_resource_name;The file contains an unknown PE resource name possibly indicative of a packer;1;
raises_exception;One or more processes crashed;1;
allocates_rwx;Allocates read-write-execute memory (usually to unpack itself);2;
protection_rx;Changes read-write memory protection to read-execute (probably to avoid detection when setting all RWX flags at the same time);2;
packer_entropy;The binary likely contains encrypted or compressed data indicative of a packer;2;
